SixNines is a 24x7 monitor of your website
availability. Just login, add one of your endpoints,
and in a few minutes you get a detailed report.
We ping all websites a few times per minute.

%p
  %form{:method=>'get', :action=>'/'}
    %fieldset
      %input{:type=>'text', :name=>'q', :size => '35', :placeholder => 'Your keyword for URI', :value=>query}/
      %button{:type=>'submit'}>Search

- if query
  - if found.empty?
    %p
      Nothing! Sorry about that.
  - else
    %p
      Found by
      ='"' + query + '":'
    %ul
      - found.each do |e|
        %li
          =EpUri.new(e).to_html
          =EpBadge.new(e).to_html

- if !flips.empty?
  %p
    Recent
    =flips.size
    flips:
  - flips.each do |e|
    %p
      =EpUri.new(e).to_html
      =EpBadge.new(e).to_html
      =ActionView::Base.new.time_ago_in_words(e.to_h[:flipped]) + ' ago'
